	lock. (#350605, reported by Wouter Bolsterlee, patch by
	Chris Wilson)

2006-08-10  Michael Natterer  <mitch@imendio.com>

	* gdk/quartz/gdkwindow-quartz.c
	(gdk_window_maximize)
	(gdk_window_unmaximize)
	(gdk_window_iconify)
