2006-05-12  Alexander Larsson  <alexl@redhat.com>

	* gtk/gtkrecentmanager.c:
	Fix build errors.
	
	* gtk/gtk.symbols:
	* demos/gtk-demo/printing.c:
	* gtk/gtkprintoperation-win32.c:
	* gtk/gtkprintoperation.[ch]:
	* gtk/gtkprintsettings.[ch]: 
