	* gtk/gen-paper-names.c: Add a prefix to gettext msgids.

	* gtk/paper_names_offsets.c: Regenerated.
	
	* gtk/gtkpapersize.c (gtk_paper_size_get_display_name):
	Use g_strip_context() to strip the prefix.

