        * gdk/quartz/gdkevents-quartz.c:
        (select_thread_func):
        (got_fd_activity):
        (poll_func):
        (gdk_event_translate):
        Make the poll func work with real file descriptors.
        We do this by creating a thread which calls poll and then
        signals the main thread using a run loop source.
        
