	* gdk/gdkevents.c (gdk_event_new): fix missing hash table 
	initialization.

Tue Dec  6 10:32:17 2005  Tim Janik  <timj@gtk.org>

	* gtk/gtkstatusbar.c: ported memchunk uses to g_slice, so the code
	compiles again.

