	* gtk/gtktreeview.c (gtk_tree_view_button_press): Be more 
	careful about initializing cell_area.  (#319382, Tommi
	Komulainen)

	* gtk/gtkcombobox.c (gtk_combo_box_key_press): Don't eat
	Ctrl-PageUp/PageDown.  (#318670, Christian Neumair)

